quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Tuaa-seen-meem
  26,2,Yeh aayaten roshan kitab ki hain
  26,3,Inn kay eman na laaney per shayad aap to apni jaan kho den gay
  26,4,Agar hum chahatay to inn per aasman say koi aisi nishani utartay kay jiss kay samney inn ki gardaney khum ho jatin
  26,5,Aur inn kay pass rehman ki taraf say jo bhi naee naseehat aaee yeh uss say roo-gardani kerney walay bann gaye
  26,6,Inn logon ney jhutlaya hai abb inn kay pass jaldi say iss ki khabren aajyen gi jiss kay sath woh maskhara pann ker rahey hain
  26,7,Kiya enhon ney zamin per nazaren nahi daalen? Kay hum ney iss mein her tarah kay nafees joray kiss qadar ugaye hain
  26,8,Be-shak iss mein yaqeenan nishani hai aur inn mein kay aksar log momin nahi hain
  26,9,Aur tera rab yaqeenan wohi ghalib aur meharbaan hai